nodes.bodyText:
Let's say that if a user calls:
DefaultServletOutputStream stream = ...
stream.write(1);
stream.write(2);
The first stream.write(1); call will close the response stream writer by calling response.getResponseWriter().close();
So 2 cannot be written. Isn't it?

